-- Openwave says it's reviewing Harbinger proposal
-- 
-- Thu Dec 28, 2006 5:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/28/us-openwave-idUSWEN163620061228

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Openwave Systems Inc. OPWV.O, a maker of communications software, said on Thursday that it is reviewing a proposal by Harbinger Capital Partners to elect two directors to Openwave's board. 

 Openwave said its board of directors would respond shortly to Harbinger's proposal, which will be voted on when Openwave holds its annual shareholder meeting on January 17.